data.description: Many updates have been made to this already MOVE-IN READY, ALL BRICK ranch! Situated on a half acre, cul-de-sac lot sits this 3 bed, 2 bath open concept home with large bonus room that could serve as a 4th bedroom. Large living room W/ vaulted ceilings is open to the spacious kitchen complete with breakfast bar, island, stainless steel appliances and 2 pantries. Off the kitchen is the dining area and access to the covered back porch complete with ceiling fan. Down the hall is the laundry room,, large storage room under the stairs, linen closet, 2 spacious bedrooms with double closets, nicely updated full bath and the generously sized master bedroom complete with huge walk-in closet, updated full bath. The half acre lot extends well beyond the fenced area and hosts a covered porch with ceiling fan, motion lights and extended concrete patio. Updates per the Seller: New water heater (2023),privacy fence (2023), Mohawk flooring (2023), paint (2023), light fixtures in master bath (2023), Shiplap on Breakfast Bar Wall (2023)MUST SEE home! Seller is a Licensed Realtor
